  "original_title": "Green Eco Lodge  \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dd2\u0dad \u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0da7 \u0d85\u0dba\u0dad\u0dca \u0db6\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dc4\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "It is confirmed that Green Eco Lodge belongs to Rohitha Rajapaksa",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been confirmed that the Green Eco Lodge luxury hotel complex located on the border of Sinharaja Forest in Kolonna Police Domain belongs to Mr. Rohitha Rajapaksa, the third son of former President Mahanda Rajapaksa.",
        "On May 10, some people set fire to this hotel complex and four suspects involved in it have been arrested by the Colonna Police.",
        "After this hotel complex was set on fire, it was reported that it belongs to Mr. Yoshita Rajapaksa, the second son of Mr. Mahanda Rajapaksa.",
        "However, he denied the reports but did not claim that it belonged to his brother.",
        "There are no information reports that Mr. Rohitha Rajapakse has been engaged in any kind of work till now."
      ],
